WEBVTT

00:00.934 --> 00:02.303
Previously on "The Path"...

00:02.336 --> 00:04.172
- I'm moving into the city.

00:04.205 --> 00:05.615
I don't want to talk about it.
I've already decided.

00:05.639 --> 00:07.141
It's a done thing.

00:07.175 --> 00:09.443
- I would like to invite you
to climb to 2R.

00:09.477 --> 00:11.445
- Are you serious?

00:11.479 --> 00:12.446
- I'd be humbled
to be your guide.

00:12.480 --> 00:14.215
- I just came from the auction.

00:14.248 --> 00:15.616
- What did he buy it for?
- Five.

00:15.649 --> 00:18.286
- $5 million?
- We don't have $5 million.

00:18.319 --> 00:19.653
- I need you to run this

00:19.687 --> 00:21.231
for industrial
pollutants and chemicals, okay?

00:21.255 --> 00:22.356
Bill it to the Meyers case.

00:22.390 --> 00:24.192
- Under what?
- Offset.

00:24.225 --> 00:26.260
- Can you help me
with something?

00:26.294 --> 00:28.162
Cut it off.

00:28.196 --> 00:30.064
- He must have fallen.

00:30.098 --> 00:32.700
This puts the entire
movement in jeopardy.

00:32.732 --> 00:34.535
I want you to think about Eddie.

00:34.568 --> 00:36.370
Let him walk away.

00:36.404 --> 00:38.072
I can only see his back now,

00:38.106 --> 00:39.607
where the lightning hit him.

00:39.640 --> 00:41.775
- He was struck by lightning
in Peru.

00:41.809 --> 00:45.313
- How did you know?

00:45.346 --> 00:46.680
- It was Eddie!

00:46.714 --> 00:48.416
Eddie Lane was
on the mountain with Steve.

00:48.449 --> 00:51.051
Eddie Lane.

